
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Demon Monsters Entering the Abyss</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        img {
            display: block;
            max-width: 50%;
            height: auto;
            margin: auto; /* Centers the image horizontally */
        }
        h1, p {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome my fellow Demon Monsters</h1>
        <img src="https://underworldlarp.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/demon.png" alt="Demon Monsters Entering the Abyss" style="width:50%;"> <!-- Adjusted width to make image smaller -->
        <p>
            As the gates of the abyss open, a legion of demon monsters begin their descent into the unknown. 
            These creatures, born from the darkest corners of the universe, are drawn to the abyss's infinite 
            darkness, seeking to claim its ancient powers.
        </p>
        <% demon_toys = ["Pitchfork", "Flamethrower", "Crossbow", "Mace"] %>
        
        <p>
            The air thickens with a palpable sense of dread and anticipation as these monstrous beings, 
            each more terrifying than the last, step over the threshold between worlds. With eyes glowing 
            and fangs bared, they march into the abyss, ready to confront whatever mysteries and challenges 
            lie within.
        </p>
        <p> 
        There are <%= demon_toys.count %> demon toys you can pick up when you enter the abyss with us. Choose wisely. 
        </p>
        <ul>
        <%j for toy in demon_toys%>
        <li> <%= toy %> </li>
        <% end %>
        </ul>
        
    </div>
</body>
</html>

